# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
debug
target

# Project-local CARGO_HOME set by the nix dev shell (see nix/devshell.nix).
# Unrooted: CARGO_HOME is relative, so running cargo from a subdirectory creates
# one *there* — a ~200 MB tree that would otherwise be staged by `git add -A`.
.cargo-home/

# Nix build symlinks
/result
/result-*

# Agent runtime state (episodic log + semantic memory)
.agent/

# Per-repo search index + freshness manifest (the SearchBackend seam)
.agent-seddon/

# Never commit secrets
*api-key*
*.key

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
# Contains mutation testing data
**/mutants.out*/

# RustRover
#  JetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
#  be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
#  and can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
#  option (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
#.idea/

# dhat leak-test heap profiles (generated by `cargo test --features dhat-heap`)
dhat-heap.json
